item.title: West Coast FG Club, 3 time champs!
item.description: Origin story There is nothing else more pleasurable than waking up the morning of competition day in a dreamy hotel. Nerves get the best of you…or maybe it’s just the coffee. You have to sprint toward the loo. In your zen, 18 back to back eagles sink and all the podium glory is owned to you. West Coast FootGolf Club (WC) knows a little thing or two about back to back.
